text: Cephalostenus elegans is a species of darkling beetles in the subfamily Tenebrioninae. It is found in Greece. == References == == External links == * Cephalostenus elegans at Fauna Europaea Category:Tenebrioninae Category:Beetles described in 1832 Category:Beetles of Europe Category:Taxa named by Gaspard Auguste Brullé
